@0=~"I hope this is important, slave. The meetings are becoming increasingly... difficult."~
@1=~"I come bearing news. You should come back to the Tower soon, it is about to happen."~
@2=~"So soon? She got through to... Lady M.? That is unexpected."~
@3=~"Not quite, my lord, but the passageways are becoming more stable... and closer to the target. Caustus and his... substance are making great progress."~
@4=~"Very well. I think things here are... stable. The baron does not look beyond the boundaries of the city too often. He is the literal opposite of Mephistopheles."~
@5=~"Yes, my lord. I need to run now. The interrogation team will be nearby soon and I need to reunite with them."~
@6=~"Ah." The fiend pauses. "Are the interrogations not finished? Then the progress is not quite *as* fast, isn't it? Go, and I will join you all, soon."~
@8=~Continue.~